<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Storyboard 1 — Karim</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #f5f0e8; }
    h1, h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
    .top-bar { background-color: #111; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; padding: 10px 0; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .top-bar a { color: #c9a84c; text-decoration: none; }
    .top-bar a:hover { color: #f5f0e8; }
    .label { font-size: 0.72rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: #c9a84c; font-weight: 600; }
    .persona-card { background-color: #2a2a2a; border-left: 3px solid #c9a84c; padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .persona-card h5 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #c9a84c; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .persona-card li, .persona-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #bbb; }
    .step-label { font-size: 0.7rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #c9a84c; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .step-card { background-color: #2a2a2a; border: 1px solid #333; }
    .mockup { background-color: #111; padding: 18px; min-height: 200px; }
    .caption { padding: 16px 18px; }
    .caption h6 { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 0.92rem; }
    .caption p { font-size: 0.83rem; color: #aaa; margin: 0; }
    /* mockup pieces */
    .mn { background:#1a1a1a; height:28px; border-radius:2px; margin-bottom:10px; display:flex; align-items:center; padding:0 10px; }
    .mn-logo { font-size:0.65rem; color:#f5f0e8; font-weight:600; }
    .mn-link { font-size:0.6rem; color:#888; margin-left:auto; }
    .mh { background:#111; border-radius:2px; padding:12px; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .mh-h { height:8px; background:#f5f0e8; border-radius:1px; width:55%; margin-bottom:5px; }
    .mh-s { height:5px; background:#555; border-radius:1px; width:75%; margin-bottom:10px; }
    .mh-btn { height:18px; background:#1a6b3a; border-radius:2px; width:28%; }
    .mf { background:#111; border-radius:2px; padding:12px; }
    .mf-lbl { height:6px; background:#c9a84c; border-radius:1px; width:35%; margin-bottom:4px; opacity:0.7; }
    .mf-inp { height:20px; background:#2a2a2a; border:1px solid #444; border-radius:2px; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .mf-btn { height:22px; background:#1a6b3a; border-radius:2px; display:flex; align-items:center; padding:0 8px; margin-top:4px; }
    .mf-btn span { font-size:0.6rem; color:#fff; }
    .mconfirm { background:#1a6b3a; border-radius:2px; padding:8px 10px; margin-top:10px; }
    .mconfirm span { font-size:0.6rem; color:#fff; }
    .arrow { color: #c9a84c; font-size: 1.4rem; text-align: center; padding-top: 80px; }
    .bottom-links { font-size: 0.82rem; border-top: 1px solid #333; padding-top: 20px; margin-top: 40px; display: flex; gap: 28px; }
    .bottom-links a { text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="top-bar">
  <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between">
    <a href="../index.html">&larr; Portfolio</a>
    <span style="color:#555;">Assignment 2 — Storyboard 1 of 2</span>
    <a href="storyboard2.html">Storyboard 2 &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container py-5">
  <p class="label">SEG3125 — Assignment 2</p>
  <h1 style="font-size:2.2rem; margin-bottom:6px;">Storyboard 1 — Karim</h1>
  <p style="color:#888; font-size:0.9rem; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Dark theme &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Goal: Book a fade online without calling</p>

  <div class="persona-card">
    <h5>Karim, 21 — University Student</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Tech-savvy, uses his phone for almost everything</li>
      <li>Values speed — gets frustrated by anything with too many steps</li>
      <li>Goes to barbershops occasionally, no regular spot yet</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin:0;"><strong style="color:#f5f0e8;">Goal:</strong> Book a fade appointment for Saturday morning without calling.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row g-3">
    <div class="col-md-3 col-10 mx-auto mx-md-0">
      <p class="step-label">Step 01</p>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mn"><span class="mn-logo">PrestigeCuts</span><span class="mn-link">Book</span></div>
          <div class="mh"><div class="mh-h"></div><div class="mh-s"></div><div class="mh-btn"></div></div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:5px;margin-top:8px;">
            <div style="flex:1;height:45px;background:#2a2a2a;border-radius:2px;border-left:2px solid #1a6b3a;"></div>
            <div style="flex:1;height:45px;background:#2a2a2a;border-radius:2px;border-left:2px solid #1a6b3a;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="caption"><h6>Lands on homepage</h6><p>Sees the hero and service cards. Clicks "Book a Cut".</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-1 d-none d-md-block arrow">&rarr;</div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-10 mx-auto mx-md-0">
      <p class="step-label">Step 02</p>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mn"><span class="mn-logo">PrestigeCuts</span></div>
          <div class="mf">
            <div class="mf-lbl"></div><div class="mf-inp"></div>
            <div class="mf-lbl"></div><div class="mf-inp"></div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:5px;">
              <div style="flex:1;"><div class="mf-lbl"></div><div class="mf-inp"></div></div>
              <div style="flex:1;"><div class="mf-lbl"></div><div class="mf-inp"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="mf-btn"><span>Confirm Booking</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="caption"><h6>Fills booking form</h6><p>Picks Fade &amp; Taper, Marcus, Saturday 10 AM. Submits.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-1 d-none d-md-block arrow">&rarr;</div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-10 mx-auto mx-md-0">
      <p class="step-label">Step 03</p>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mn"><span class="mn-logo">PrestigeCuts</span></div>
          <div class="mf" style="margin-top:10px;">
            <div style="height:5px;background:#555;width:80%;border-radius:1px;margin-bottom:8px;"></div>
            <div style="height:5px;background:#555;width:60%;border-radius:1px;margin-bottom:16px;"></div>
            <div class="mconfirm"><span>Booked! Karim — Fade &amp; Taper on Saturday at 10 AM.</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="caption"><h6>Sees confirmation</h6><p>Green message appears instantly. Done in under a minute.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom-links">
    <a href="../service-site.html" style="color:#c9a84c;">View Live Site &rarr;</a>
    <a href="storyboard2.html" style="color:#666;">Storyboard 2 &rarr;</a>
    <a href="../index.html" style="color:#666;">Portfolio &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</div>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
